## `POST /v1/embeddings`

### Response
```json
{
  "object": "list",
  "data": [
    { "index": 0, "object": "embedding", "embedding": [0.012, -0.041, ...] }
  ],
  "model": "text-embedding-3-small",
  "usage": { "prompt_tokens": 12, "total_tokens": 12 }
}
```

[Docs](https://platform.openai.com/docs/api-reference/embeddings)

